1.description:
The Unruggables Phoenix Punks is the first NFT collection of the $WGMI Community Token (ERC20 on the Ethereum Blockchain). 
 The collection consist of 888 unique Phoenix Punks. We felt that the Phoenix represent how we came from the ashes as a community after the token was originally ruggued by the creator.  
 Royalties from secondary sales of the Phoenix Punks NFT's will buy $WGMI token from Uniswap and deposit Liquidity into the ETH/WGMI pair that will be locked forever.

 The collection consist of 888 unique Phoenix Punks. We felt that the Phoenix represent how we came from the ashes as a community after the token was originally ruggued by the creator.  
 Royalties from secondary sales of the Phoenix Punks NFT's will buy $WGMI token from Uniswap and deposit Liquidity into the ETH/WGMI pair that will be locked forever.

 The collection consist of 888 unique Phoenix Punks. We felt that the Phoenix represent how we came from the ashes as a community after the token was originally ruggued by the creator.  
 Royalties from secondary sales of the Phoenix Punks NFT's will buy $WGMI token from Uniswap and deposit Liquidity into the ETH/WGMI pair that will be locked forever.

 The collection consist of 888 unique Phoenix Punks. We felt that the Phoenix represent how we came from the ashes as a community after the token was originally ruggued by the creator.  
 Royalties from secondary sales of the Phoenix Punks NFT's will buy $WGMI token from Uniswap and deposit Liquidity into the ETH/WGMI pair that will be locked forever.

 The collection consist of 888 unique Phoenix Punks. We felt that the Phoenix represent how we came from the ashes as a community after the token was originally ruggued by the creator.  
 Royalties from secondary sales of the Phoenix Punks NFT's will buy $WGMI token from Uniswap and deposit Liquidity into the ETH/WGMI pair that will be locked forever.

 The collection consist of 888 unique Phoenix Punks. We felt that the Phoenix represent how we came from the ashes as a community after the token was originally ruggued by the creator.  
 Royalties from secondary sales of the Phoenix Punks NFT's will buy $WGMI token from Uniswap and deposit Liquidity into the ETH/WGMI pair that will be locked forever.
